{
  "action": "pipeline",
  "pipeline_id": "hiring-workflow",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "name": "Hiring Workflow",
  "description": "Hiring workflow that turns a role brief into a JD draft, schedules interview slots, and produces an evaluation memo for talent_culture and line_manager review.",
  "_migration_note": "v2: Typed Flow format (role/produces/consumes).",
  "context": {
    "mission_id": "",
    "tenant_slug": "",
    "role_name": "",
    "role_domain": "",
    "candidate_profile_path": "active/shared/tmp/hiring-candidate-profile-{{mission_id}}.json",
    "jd_draft_path": "active/shared/tmp/hiring-jd-draft-{{mission_id}}.md",
    "interview_schedule_path": "active/shared/tmp/hiring-interview-schedule-{{mission_id}}.json",
    "evaluation_path": "active/shared/tmp/hiring-evaluation-{{mission_id}}.md"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "preflight",
      "role": "gate",
      "op": "core:include",
      "params": { "fragment": "fragments/browser-runtime-preflight.json" }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_start",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "🧑‍💼 Hiring workflow start for mission {{mission_id}} role={{role_name}} domain={{role_domain}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "read_candidate_profile",
      "role": "source",
      "op": "system:read_file",
      "produces": { "channel": "candidate_profile", "type": "CandidateProfile" },
      "params": {
        "path": "{{candidate_profile_path}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "draft_jd",
      "role": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "consumes": "candidate_profile",
      "produces": { "channel": "jd_draft", "type": "JobDescriptionDraft" },
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下の candidate profile と role 情報をもとに、採用 JD の下書きを Markdown で作成してください。talent_culture と line_manager がレビューできる実務的な内容にしてください。\n\n必須セクション:\n# Hiring Workflow\n## 募集背景\n## 役割概要\n## 必須要件\n## 歓迎要件\n## 面接で確認する観点\n## オファー判断での注意点\n\n要件:\n- 役割の責務を明確にする\n- 判断基準を箇条書きにする\n- 採用可否の最終決定は人間承認前提であることを明示する",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{role_name}}", "{{role_domain}}", "{{candidate_profile}}"]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_jd_draft",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:write_artifact",
      "consumes": "jd_draft",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{jd_draft_path}}",
        "content": "{{jd_draft}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "schedule_interviews",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "calendar:create_event",
      "params": {
        "calendar_names": ["仕事"],
        "title": "Hiring interview: {{role_name}}",
        "start_date": "{{interview_start_iso}}",
        "end_date": "{{interview_end_iso}}",
        "location": "Zoom / Google Meet",
        "description": "Kyberion hiring workflow mission {{mission_id}} for {{role_name}} (domain: {{role_domain}})."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_schedule",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:write_file",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{interview_schedule_path}}",
        "content": {
          "kind": "hiring-interview-schedule",
          "mission_id": "{{mission_id}}",
          "tenant_slug": "{{tenant_slug}}",
          "role_name": "{{role_name}}",
          "role_domain": "{{role_domain}}",
          "calendar": "仕事",
          "interview_start": "{{interview_start_iso}}",
          "interview_end": "{{interview_end_iso}}"
        },
        "format": "json"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "draft_evaluation",
      "role": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "consumes": ["candidate_profile", "jd_draft"],
      "produces": { "channel": "evaluation_memo", "type": "HiringEvaluationMemo" },
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下の candidate profile と JD draft をもとに、面接評価メモを Markdown で作成してください。talent_culture / line_manager が評価観点を共有する前提です。\n\n必須セクション:\n# Hiring Evaluation\n## 候補者概要\n## 評価観点\n## 強み\n## 懸念点\n## 追加で聞く質問\n## 次のアクション\n\n要件:\n- 候補者の事実と推測を分ける\n- 評価の根拠を明確にする\n- 最終採用判断は人間承認前提であることを明記する",
        "context": [
          "{{mission_id}}",
          "{{role_name}}",
          "{{role_domain}}",
          "{{candidate_profile}}",
          "{{jd_draft}}"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_evaluation",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:write_artifact",
      "consumes": "evaluation_memo",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{evaluation_path}}",
        "content": "{{evaluation_memo}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_done",
      "role": "sink",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "✅ Hiring workflow complete: {{jd_draft_path}}, {{interview_schedule_path}}, {{evaluation_path}}"
      }
    }
  ]
}
